headline.print_headline: UK Lawmakers Pass Symbolic Motion on Palestinian State
headline.main: UK Lawmakers Pass Symbolic Motion on Palestinian State

lead_paragraph: British lawmakers voted on Monday to recognize Palestine as a state, a move that will not alter government policy, but carries symbolic value as Palestinians pursue international recognition.
